{"type": "article", "id": 27857, "title": "可以做花瓶的路由器", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-07T06:51:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021519271D2KH8hgM3zBO9v5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>路由器已经成为家中必不可少的电子产品之一，然而将实用性和装饰性结合在一起的设计却非常少见。德国瓷器品牌 <a href=\"https://www.rosenthal.de/en/\">Rosenthal</a> 委托设计师 <a href=\"http://iamferdinand.com/\">Ferdinand Povel</a> 设计了一款可以用做花瓶的路由器 PorceLAN，希望可以打破人们对路由器的刻板印象。PorceLAN 的上半部份可以当作花瓶使用，路由器的基础组件则隐藏在下半部分。两者通过磁性锁相连互不影响，既简洁又美观。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151924Gev4ZNXyn3LmOsl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151925frJ54Bx0puyAN9ES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151926koyx3DwG5CV7iIj9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54889976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151926WrtBoShqZbYfzRAu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}